description.narrative: UNICEF advocacy and technical assistance resulted in substantial progress in the MCH-MIS project - including the establishment of the platform, standards for indicators, and data exchange, as well as adoption of the unique ID by theNational Action Plan for Health Information and Management System. This will amplify the impact of the project to benefit a large number of health workers, managers, and health facilities across the country to improve service delivery and decision making. Additionally, UNICEF supported the testing of strengthened nutrition data collection in MCH-MIS in Qinghai Province. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:01/02/2021
